trans-unit.source: Provides the data for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Udostępnia dane dla <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated"> </xref> zdarzeń.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Ta klasa nie może być dziedziczona.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A tracking service that implements the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification> interface raises a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> event to notify the runtime tracking infrastructure that the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for a particular workflow <xref:System.Type> has changed.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Usługa śledzenia, która implementuje <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>interfejsu zgłasza <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>zdarzenie, aby powiadomić infrastrukturze środowiska uruchomieniowego śledzenia który <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>dla określonego przepływu pracy <xref:System.Type>został zmieniony.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service uses a ProfileUpdatedEventArgs to provide the workflow <xref:System.Type> and the new <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> to the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Usługa śledzenia używa ProfileUpdatedEventArgs zapewnienie przepływu pracy <xref:System.Type>i nowych <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>do śledzenia infrastruktury środowiska uruchomieniowego.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> uses a ProfileUpdatedEventArgs when it raises the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileUpdated?displayProperty=fullName> event.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>używa ProfileUpdatedEventArgs, gdy zgłasza <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileUpdated?displayProperty=fullName>zdarzeń.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService.ProfileUpdated?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: When it receives a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure will update the tracking profile for the specified workflow <xref:System.Type> in its profile cache.
trans-unit.target: Po otrzymaniu <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>zdarzenia śledzenia infrastruktury środowiska uruchomieniowego spowoduje zaktualizowanie profilu śledzenia dla określonego przepływu pracy <xref:System.Type>w swojej pamięci podręcznej profilu.</xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: If you use this constructor when you raise a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> event inside a tracking service, you must explicitly set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli używasz tego konstruktora, gdy zostanie podniesiony do <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>zdarzeń wewnątrz usługi śledzenia, należy jawnie ustawić <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs"></xref> class that specifies a new <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> for the specified workflow <xref:System.Type>.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs"> </xref> klasy, która określa nowy <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> dla określonego przepływu pracy <xref:System.Type>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs> is created with <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> set to the specified <xref:System.Type> and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A> set to the specified profile.
trans-unit.target: Nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs>jest tworzony z <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>ustawiona na określony <xref:System.Type>i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A>ustawioną określonego profilu.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.TrackingProfile%2A> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileRemovedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of workflow for which the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> has changed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>Przepływu pracy, dla którego <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> został zmieniony.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The new <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: The new <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the new <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> for the workflow Type.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera lub ustawia nowe <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> dla typu przepływu pracy.

trans-unit.source: When the runtime tracking infrastructure receives a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated> event it will update its profile cache with the new <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> for the workflow <xref:System.Type> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Gdy infrastrukturze środowiska uruchomieniowego śledzenia odbiera <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>zdarzenia spowoduje zaktualizowanie pamięci podręcznej profil z nowego <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>przepływu pracy <xref:System.Type>określonego przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ProfileUpdatedEventArgs.WorkflowType%2A> </xref:System.Type> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.IProfileNotification.ProfileUpdated>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"></xref> for the workflow type.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> dla typu przepływu pracy.

trans-unit.target: Pobiera lub ustawia <xref:System.Type>przepływu pracy, którego <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile"> </xref> powinien zostać zaktualizowany.</xref:System.Type>
